summary: A small mod that changes the looks of many of the NPCs in Skyrim, just to make playing it for the thousandth time feel more "New".
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]A New Look - Fresh Faces
[/size][size=3]What does it do?
[/size]It simply changes the looks of the most common/most visited NPCs. So far I have focused on Whiterun, as the place every character will visit a fair bit.

[size=3]Bugs?
[/size]All this mod changes is the looks and outfits, so there shouldn't be any bugs except for some NPCs looking a little ill, but this is rare and being fixed. If there is a NPC you don't like from this mod, tell me why in the comments and I'll try to change them or if there is a NPC you want changing in the base game, again, tell me and I'll see what I can do.
author: Pelagius the Geek
